# 🚀 Gyros Siren Home

An all-in-one Discord bot + web dashboard featuring moderation, economy, giveaways, boss battles, and advanced channel tools like cloning and photo scanning.

---

## ✨ Features

### 🛡️ Moderation
- Ban, kick, mute, clear messages
- Automod (invite link protection)

### 💰 Economy System
- Daily rewards
- Collect system
- Gambling
- Leaderboard
- Player-to-player transfers

### 🎉 Giveaways
- Start / end giveaways
- Auto winner selection
- Reroll system

### ⚔️ Boss Battles
- Spawn bosses in chat
- Team damage system
- Coin rewards

### 📸 Channel Tools
- Clone messages between channels
- Scan and extract images only

### 🌐 Web Dashboard
- Live command list
- Clean UI
- Animated star background

---

## 📦 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/gyros-siren-home
cd gyros-siren-home
npm install
